{"tid":1428479,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"詢問法律意見：請問佢咁的言論係咪煽動他人犯罪","createTime":"2019-08-07T09:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T09:59:18.000Z","uid":182096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d54cdd3d1946ff327b1414354f6a307e7246991a","tid":1428479,"uid":182096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WWHuRMU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWWHuRMU.png&h=28fc9c8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請問佢咁的言論係咪煽動他人犯罪？ <br />\n<br />\n「在香港的普通法和成文法裡，他人試圖、串謀、煽惑或教唆他人犯罪，均是違法行為。根據《刑事訴訟程序條例》 第89條 ：「任何人協助，教唆，慫使或促致另一人犯任何罪行，即屬就同一罪行有罪」，而《刑事罪行條例》第10 條則規定，任何人作出、企圖作出、準備作出或與任何人串謀作出具煽動意圖的作為，或發表煽動文字或煽動刊物，即屬違法。」<br />\n<br />\nCitation: <a href=\"https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2018-08/23/28976.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkhk.com%2Farticle%2F2018-08%2F23%2F28976.html&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ5BhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=7ef43842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2018-08/23/28976.html</a>"},{"pid":"421424e4533e208193fa7b795a6a78755a67e1b8","tid":1428479,"uid":182096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d54cdd3d1946ff327b1414354f6a307e7246991a","tid":1428479,"uid":182096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WWHuRMU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWWHuRMU.png&h=28fc9c8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請問佢咁的言論係咪煽動他人犯罪？ <br />\n<br />\n「在香港的普通法和成文法裡，他人試圖、串謀、煽惑或教唆他人犯罪，均是違法行為。根據《刑事訴訟程序條例》 第89條 ：「任何人協助，教唆，慫使或促致另一人犯任何罪行，即屬就同一罪行有罪」，而《刑事罪行條例》第10 條則規定，任何人作出、企圖作出、準備作出或與任何人串謀作出具煽動意圖的作為，或發表煽動文字或煽動刊物，即屬違法。」<br />\n<br />\nCitation: <a href=\"https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2018-08/23/28976.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkhk.com%2Farticle%2F2018-08%2F23%2F28976.html&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ5BhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=7ef43842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2018-08/23/28976.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:56:30.000Z","msg":"人地拎黎觀星，佢拎黎射人眼，我好驚驚呀 <br />\n依家係咪引起埋公眾恐慌？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa0f3b0d0bfe6f5bdf2ffb2748c775d51f664a5","tid":1428479,"uid":182096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:59:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁鍾意以言入罪<br />\n又唔見你拉佢地？ <br />\n<br />\n</span>"}]}